網路加速，網路環境最佳化 – SG TCP Optimizer

丹楓 ⋅ 2 則評論 




SG TCP Optimizer 是一款小巧、強大的網路加速工具，TCP Optimizer 可透過調整系統的 TTL、TCP/IP、寬頻延遲、MTU、接收緩衝區(RWIN)、最大傳輸單元(MTU)、瀏覽器(IE)併發連接數、功能變數名稱解析優先順序、功能變數名稱解析錯誤暫存時間等重要參數來有效最佳化網路環境，提升上網速度！並可檢測網路允許的最大傳輸單元大小和網路延遲，計算合適的接收緩衝區，並提供網路參數相關的登錄檔編輯功能。無論您是網路高手還是普通菜鳥，都可以透過 TCP Optimizer 輕輕鬆鬆地設定最佳化網速，加速上網。

 

【軟體名稱】：SG TCP Optimizer 4.0.6 – 網路加速，網路環境最佳化
【軟體大小】：680 KB
【作業系統】：Windows All
【官方網站】：http://www.speedguide.net/
【語言種類】：英文
The TCP Optimizer is a free, easy Windows program that provides an intuitive interface for tuning and optimizing your Internet connection. There is no installation required, just download and run as administrator. The program can aid both the novice and the advanced user in tweaking related TCP/IP parameters in Windows, making it easy to tune your system to the type of Internet connection used. The tool uses advanced algorithms, and the bandwidth*delay product to find the best TCP Window for your specific connection speed. It provides for easy tuning of all related TCP/IP parameters, such as MTU, RWIN, and even advanced ones like QoS and ToS/Diffserv prioritization.
官方下載連結：
最新版→ [4.0.6]





